description: Copper Fit Energy Unisex Crew Length Compression Socks provide superior support for your arch, feet and calves. The Energy Compression Socks reduce pain and swelling caused from prolonged sitting or standing. Equipped with a fully cushioned foot bed, these socks are built for all day comfort. Great for running, cycling, sports, hiking, travel, flights, pregnancy and every day wear. Make sure to order the right size - Small/Medium fits Men's shoe size 6-9 and Women's shoe size 7-10; Large/X-Large fits Men's shoe size 9-12 and Women's shoe size 10-13.
